wly added","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":"feature, has a unique ID (or a unique promote ID if in use). Failure to provide unique IDs will result"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"text":"in a ","type":"text"},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"map-loading-error"},{"type":"text","text":"."}]},{"name":"Note","type":"aside","style":"note","content":[{"inlineContent":[{"text":"The method allows the user to provide a data ID, which will be returned as the ","type":"text"},{"code":"dataId","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":" parameter in the"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"source-data-loaded"},{"text":" event. However, it’s important to note that multiple partial updates can be queued","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"text":"for the same GeoJSON source when ongoing source parsing is taking place. In these cases, the partial","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"text":"updates will be applied to the source in batches. Only the data ID provided in the most recent call within","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"each batch will be included in the ","type":"text"},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"source-data-loaded"},{"text":" event. If no data ID is provided in the most recent","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"text":"call, the data ID in the ","type":"text"},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"source-data-loaded"},{"type":"text","text":"event will be null."}],"type":"paragraph"}]},{"type":"aside","name":"Throws","content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"","type":"text"},{"type":"reference","isActive":true,"identifier":"doc:\/\/com.mapbox.MapboxMaps\/documentation\/MapboxMaps\/StyleError"},{"type":"text","text":" if there is a problem removing features from the source."}]}],"style":"note"}],"kind":"content"}],"abstract":[{"text":"Remove features from a GeoJSON style source.","type":"text"}],"kind":"symbol","variants":[{"paths":["\/documentation\/mapboxmaps\/stylemanager\/remo